===Noun phrase===
'''[[weapon]] of [[mass]] [[destruction]]''' (''plural:'' '''weapons of mass destruction''')

# A [[chemical]], [[biological]] or [[nuclear]] [[weapon]] that is designed to cause [[death]] or serious [[injury]] to large numbers of [[civilian]]s.

